### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `message-visualizer:open` | Open visualizer for current session |
| `message-visualizer:entry` | View specific entry by ID |
| `message-visualizer:compare` | Compare layers for selected message |
| `message-visualizer:export` | Export session as JSON |

### Key APIs

```typescript
// Access session
const entries = context.sessionManager.loadSession(sessionId);

// Transformation functions
import { convertToLlm } from "@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent";
import { transformMessages } from "@mariozechner/pi-ai/providers";

// Live updates
context.agent.subscribe((event) => {
  if (event.type === "message_end") visualizer.refresh();
});

// Payload capture
context.sdk.onPayload = (payload, model) => {
  visualizer.capturePayload(payload, model);
};
```

